mg3.doubanio.com/icon/u37545357-2.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "", "comment_time": "", "content": "<span class=\"short\">Boeser Sieben! 呵呵。</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "1060715401", "nick_name": "跑马溜溜滴阿三", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/141838043/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal_f.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar30 rating", "comment_time": "2016-07-11", "content": "<span class=\"short\">说实话，不是特别喜欢这种类型的书，读起来比较平淡。刚开始看了一小部分，觉得读不下去了，后来是因为实在没书看了，就硬着头皮读了下去，竟然还突然起了兴趣一口气看完了它。</span>\n            "}], "reviews": []}